Following the **[March 2026 price crash](https://diamondcritics.com/diamond-prices/)**, the price gap between the G and H tiers has widened, creating a massive opportunity for value-buyers. While a G-color diamond is the "Retailer's Bait," the H-color is the "Insider's Secret."

